00:00:32.496 --> 00:00:36.660
﻿I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

00:00:51.226 --> 00:00:55.106
At the very outset we have to know

00:00:55.771 --> 00:00:58.805
that Truth is what it is.

00:01:07.623 --> 00:01:12.700
We cannot organize it, we cannot order it.

00:01:22.043 --> 00:01:27.460
And at the human level we cannot achieve it.

00:01:36.572 --> 00:01:39.864
We have become from ameba

00:01:40.065 --> 00:01:43.380
to this stage of the human beings.

00:01:51.319 --> 00:01:57.300
But still we have not reached our absolute Truth.

00:02:05.106 --> 00:02:10.140
Some people believe
this is good, some people believe that is good.

00:02:16.359 --> 00:02:22.580
So under we can decide
something or on emotional basis

00:02:22.780 --> 00:02:25.340
or on rational basis.

00:02:34.112 --> 00:02:36.820
And both are limited.

00:02:41.086 --> 00:02:44.860
Anything can be justified with rationality.

00:02:48.926 --> 00:02:52.420
Also emotionally we can justify;

00:02:52.620 --> 00:02:55.820
might be our emotional oughts.

00:03:02.266 --> 00:03:05.973
So everyone can think differently

00:03:06.666 --> 00:03:10.180
according to their own projections.

00:03:21.466 --> 00:03:25.340
So you have to go to a stage,

00:03:25.540 --> 00:03:30.500
a state where you can all
say the same to this, is the Truth.

00:03:41.172 --> 00:03:44.613
The whole humanity has to come to that state

00:03:44.813 --> 00:03:47.972
where they know this is Absolute.

00:03:56.739 --> 00:04:01.660
So we have to understand
that our evolution is not yet complete.

00:04:09.165 --> 00:04:12.700
There is one more break-through in it.

00:04:13.606 --> 00:04:15.606
One more break-through in it.

00:04:23.212 --> 00:04:27.980
This break-through is Self-Realization.

00:04:32.646 --> 00:04:35.300
Is to know your Self.

00:04:40.352 --> 00:04:44.940
To know your Self is not possible
if you work it out mentally,

00:04:45.140 --> 00:04:47.700
physically, or emotionally.

00:04:59.713 --> 00:05:03.713
After all, when we became from ameba to this stage

00:05:03.913 --> 00:05:05.913
we did not do anything.

00:05:15.133 --> 00:05:18.353
It is through the living process

00:05:18.933 --> 00:05:24.100
of evolution we have
spontaneously become human beings.

00:05:35.313 --> 00:05:40.620
So, if anything has to happen
it has to happen spontaneously.

00:05:46.226 --> 00:05:51.700
Like a seed, if you put it in the
Mother Earth it sprouts by itself.

00:05:57.246 --> 00:06:00.580
So the seed has got a built-in quality

00:06:00.780 --> 00:06:05.020
and the Mother Earth also has
contributive quality to sprout it.

00:06:21.273 --> 00:06:26.453
In the same way within us is placed the power

00:06:27.240 --> 00:06:29.340
of pure desire,

00:06:29.666 --> 00:06:33.580
which gives you that break-through.

00:06:49.493 --> 00:06:52.760
It is the power of pure desire.

00:06:56.500 --> 00:06:59.380
Whatever desires we have

00:06:59.993 --> 00:07:04.300
we do not get satisfied once they are fulfilled.

00:07:14.233 --> 00:07:18.260
We want to have food, when we
get the food we want to have clothes,

00:07:18.460 --> 00:07:22.820
when we have the clothes we want to 
have a house, then we want to have a car,

00:07:23.020 --> 00:07:27.013
then we want to have an airplane, 
and I don’t know; it goes on like that.

00:07:44.712 --> 00:07:49.220
That means in general our wants are not satiable.

00:08:00.480 --> 00:08:05.260
Then we have very dormant state,
we have a desire within us,

00:08:05.460 --> 00:08:07.590
which is a pure desire.

00:08:13.503 --> 00:08:15.700
This pure desire

00:08:15.900 --> 00:08:20.620
is to become one with the
All Pervading Subtle Power

00:08:20.820 --> 00:08:23.050
of Love.

00:08:33.900 --> 00:08:40.140
Now whatever I’m telling you, you
have to accept it as a hypothesis.

00:08:45.846 --> 00:08:50.100
And as a scientist you must keep your minds open.

00:08:58.726 --> 00:09:04.180
And if it works then we have
to believe as honest people.

00:09:11.693 --> 00:09:17.780
So this power within us lies in
a triangular bone called as sacrum.

00:09:27.020 --> 00:09:30.420
Sacrum is a Greek word meaning sacred,

00:09:30.620 --> 00:09:36.700
and it means, it means Greek people
knew that there is sacred power in it.

00:09:51.185 --> 00:09:56.060
So this power is placed in this triangular bone

00:09:56.390 --> 00:10:02.340
and is awakened as a germ

00:10:02.540 --> 00:10:07.020
or a primula in a seed, spontaneously.

00:10:20.936 --> 00:10:27.260
It pierces through six centers, ultimately
through the fontanel bone area

00:10:27.460 --> 00:10:31.980
and you start feeling a cool
breeze coming out of your head.

00:10:46.442 --> 00:10:51.390
If this center is all right then
you start feeling in your hands

00:10:51.590 --> 00:10:56.339
a kind of a beautiful soothing
cool breeze all around us.

00:11:05.293 --> 00:11:12.060
This power in the sacrum bone is
called as Kundalini in Sanskrit language.

00:11:19.740 --> 00:11:23.593
And many people in India thousands of years back

00:11:23.793 --> 00:11:28.860
have discovered about
this Kundalini in our country.

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:40.427
The word Kundalini comes from the coils,

00:11:40.627 --> 00:11:44.906
Kundalini is the coils because
it is in three and half coil.

00:11:53.940 --> 00:11:56.220
Now She is your mother.

00:11:58.420 --> 00:12:04.780
And She takes up all the troubles
to give you your second birth.

00:12:11.420 --> 00:12:14.620
So you don’t get any troubles.

00:12:19.059 --> 00:12:23.460
In Sanskrit language we call a person who

00:12:23.660 --> 00:12:29.660
knows about this All Pervading
Power of Brahma as, as dvijaha.

00:12:46.760 --> 00:12:49.780
Also a bird is called as dvidjaha.

00:12:53.720 --> 00:12:56.820
Dvi-jaha means born twice.

00:13:02.793 --> 00:13:06.460
Like a bird is first born at the egg

00:13:06.660 --> 00:13:09.980
and then it becomes like a bird.

00:13:18.946 --> 00:13:25.100
In the same way a human being is born in a closed

00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:32.860
way of ego and superego on his
brain, is the closed personality.

00:13:52.253 --> 00:13:57.980
But when Kundalini rises
and he becomes the Spirit,

00:13:58.180 --> 00:14:04.780
he becomes as different dynamic personality.

00:14:14.093 --> 00:14:17.300
He becomes that free personality.

00:14:19.480 --> 00:14:24.540
No habits can overpower him.

00:14:29.293 --> 00:14:32.380
He does not overpower anyone.

00:14:34.426 --> 00:14:37.540
And nobody can overpower him.

00:14:40.706 --> 00:14:45.420
He becomes a very
compassionate, confident personality.

00:14:51.966 --> 00:14:57.446
And he can feel the All
Pervading Power on his fingertips.

00:15:04.466 --> 00:15:09.946
Now this All Pervading Power organizes,

00:15:10.333 --> 00:15:16.300
thinks, above all it loves.

00:15:26.780 --> 00:15:30.260
So, when this connection is established,

00:15:30.699 --> 00:15:36.740
your physical problems, your emotional
problems, your mental problems,

00:15:36.940 --> 00:15:40.460
and your spiritual problems all get solved.

00:15:51.906 --> 00:15:56.060
It is not an artificial thing, it’s reality.

00:16:01.626 --> 00:16:05.460
The problem with the religion was that

00:16:05.660 --> 00:16:10.380
