01:26:06.833 --> 01:26:10.860
but you are pure Spirit.

01:26:25.231 --> 01:26:28.340
So now raise your right hand

01:26:28.713 --> 01:26:33.486
onto your heart and with 
full confidence please say,

01:26:33.687 --> 01:26:36.940
“Mother, I am the Spirit”.

01:27:01.723 --> 01:27:05.653
As I’ve told you that this Divine Power,

01:27:05.853 --> 01:27:08.853
or we may call it the All Pervading Power,

01:27:09.054 --> 01:27:13.060
is the ocean of love and compassion.

01:27:19.553 --> 01:27:23.700
It is the ocean of bliss and joy.

01:27:28.619 --> 01:27:32.700
But above all it is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:27:37.053 --> 01:27:42.860
So all your mistakes are completely 
dissolved by this great ocean.

01:27:49.906 --> 01:27:54.200
So now raise your right hand 
in the corner of your neck

01:27:54.446 --> 01:28:00.020
and your shoulder and put your head to your right.

01:28:10.999 --> 01:28:16.540
Here you have to say with full confidence,

01:28:16.740 --> 01:28:21.460
“Mother, I’m not guilty at all”, 
please say it twelve times.

01:28:23.192 --> 01:28:26.700
[UNCLEAR] Sixteen times.

01:28:48.099 --> 01:28:51.540
As I’ve told you that

01:28:51.740 --> 01:28:55.340
whether you forgive or don’t 
forgive you don’t do anything.

01:28:55.540 --> 01:28:59.440
But if we don’t
forgive then we play into wrong hands.

01:28:59.641 --> 01:29:02.740
So we have to forgive everyone.

01:29:20.402 --> 01:29:25.660
So now please put your right 
hand on your forehead across

01:29:25.860 --> 01:29:28.740
and bend your head slowly on it.

01:29:35.952 --> 01:29:38.287
Here you have to say,

01:29:38.487 --> 01:29:42.900
with full understanding,

01:29:43.100 --> 01:29:45.460
not how many times,

01:29:46.553 --> 01:29:51.300
“Mother, I forgive everyone”, from your heart.

01:30:10.584 --> 01:30:13.580
Now for your own satisfaction

01:30:14.800 --> 01:30:20.340
you have to ask forgiveness, for your
own satisfaction, without feeling guilty,

01:30:21.333 --> 01:30:23.940
without counting your mistakes.

01:30:41.925 --> 01:30:46.180
Now, so for that you put your 
hand on the back side of your head

01:30:46.380 --> 01:30:49.460
and push back your head as much as you can do.

01:30:59.478 --> 01:31:03.700
You have to say, “Oh, All Pervading Power of Love,

01:31:03.906 --> 01:31:07.240
if we have done any mistakes, please forgive us”.

01:31:20.253 --> 01:31:22.820
Now stretch your hand

01:31:28.999 --> 01:31:34.380
and put the center of your palm 
on top of your fontanel bone area.

01:31:41.712 --> 01:31:46.140
This is important, so press it 
hard, push back your fingers,

01:31:46.340 --> 01:31:49.940
and you have to move your scalp seven times.

01:31:54.878 --> 01:31:59.060
Put down your head and very slowly move.

01:32:06.527 --> 01:32:10.220
Here again I cannot take your freedom,

01:32:10.420 --> 01:32:13.527
so you have to ask for Self-Realization.

01:32:13.727 --> 01:32:19.100
You have to say seven times, 
“Mother please give me my Self-Realization”.

01:33:11.519 --> 01:33:14.980
Now please take down your hands.

01:33:18.606 --> 01:33:21.700
Please open your eyes.

01:33:25.905 --> 01:33:29.300
Now, put both the hands like this towards Me.

01:33:33.872 --> 01:33:37.100
Now, put the right hand towards Me like that.

01:33:45.065 --> 01:33:48.940
Now bend your head and see for yourself

01:33:49.140 --> 01:33:54.020
if there’s any cool breeze coming 
out of your head, with your left hand.

01:34:04.406 --> 01:34:06.780
Some people get it little hot

01:34:06.980 --> 01:34:10.020
and some people get it little far away.

01:34:18.639 --> 01:34:20.740
Now bend your…

01:34:21.966 --> 01:34:25.500
Put your left hand towards Me, 
but must bend your head.

01:34:32.293 --> 01:34:37.946
Now see from your head if there’s a
cool breeze coming with right hand.

01:34:50.040 --> 01:34:53.493
Now, put your right hand towards Me

01:34:53.893 --> 01:34:57.260
and please bend your head

01:34:57.460 --> 01:35:00.993
and see with your left hand if was 
cool breeze coming out of your head.

01:35:14.192 --> 01:35:19.300
Now, raise your both the hands 
towards the sky, push back your head.

01:35:22.406 --> 01:35:24.560
Ask a question three times,

01:35:24.760 --> 01:35:28.900
“Is this the cool breeze of the 
All Pervading Power of Love?”.

01:35:37.333 --> 01:35:40.153
Ask this question three times.

01:35:45.071 --> 01:35:47.780
You may not [UNCLEAR] of mine.

01:35:47.980 --> 01:35:52.940
“Is this the cool breeze
of the All Pervading Power of Love?”.

01:36:06.479 --> 01:36:09.020
Now put down your hands.

01:36:11.533 --> 01:36:14.500
Firstly, you’ll feel very relaxed.

01:36:18.633 --> 01:36:21.260
And thoughtlessly aware.

01:36:25.713 --> 01:36:29.380
All those who have felt the 
cool breeze out of their head

01:36:29.667 --> 01:36:34.440
or on the fingertips 
please raise both your hands.

01:36:45.726 --> 01:36:47.820
Both the hands, please.

01:36:58.819 --> 01:37:01.420
So many of you have felt it,

01:37:01.621 --> 01:37:04.900
most of you, most of you.

01:37:06.139 --> 01:37:10.420
Tomorrow again those 
who have not felt will feel it.

01:37:14.107 --> 01:37:18.180
And those who have felt will feel it better.

01:37:22.146 --> 01:37:26.780
Apart that we should not 
discuss it, arguing, it is beyond mind.

01:37:33.820 --> 01:37:36.206
Interpreter: Many felt heat coming out.

01:37:36.407 --> 01:37:38.780
