01:37:41.400 --> 01:37:44.273
You’ve much heat in the body, let it get out.

01:37:46.379 --> 01:37:50.020
Doesn’t matter. Heat will go away.

01:37:52.377 --> 01:37:55.620
Also if you don’t forgive you feel heat.

01:38:00.485 --> 01:38:03.733
You put your right hand 
like this and left hand like this.

01:38:09.245 --> 01:38:13.740
Left hand like this, like this, backward. 
