01:38:16.546 --> 01:38:20.180
Tell them they have to put like this, backward.

01:38:22.233 --> 01:38:24.700
Not like this, like this.

01:38:26.453 --> 01:38:30.740
Now you say from your heart, in your heart,

01:38:31.067 --> 01:38:34.940
“Mother, I forgive everyone”. Say from your heart.

