Cooler now?

01:38:51.420 --> 01:38:53.420
Cooler?

01:38:58.343 --> 01:39:00.239
Good, better.

01:39:00.440 --> 01:39:02.980
Now see on your head if it’s cooler.

01:39:09.812 --> 01:39:11.860
Better now?

01:39:15.146 --> 01:39:17.146
You should have.

01:39:18.306 --> 01:39:20.306
Cooler?

01:39:22.440 --> 01:39:24.440
All right?

